trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell" /> objects that are the cells of a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Representa una colección de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell" /> que se encuentran en las celdas del control <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.CellControlCollection> class represents the collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell> objects of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow> control.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.CellControlCollection> clase representa la colección de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell> objetos de un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow> control.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell> objects can be added at the end of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.CellControlCollection> collection with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.CellControlCollection.Add%2A> method or at a specified index location in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.CellControlCollection> with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.CellControlCollection.AddAt%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell> se pueden agregar objetos al final de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.CellControlCollection> colección con el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.CellControlCollection.Add%2A> método o en una ubicación de índice especificada en el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.CellControlCollection> con el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.CellControlCollection.AddAt%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: Only <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell> objects can be added to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.CellControlCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: Solo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell> se pueden agregar objetos a la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.CellControlCollection> colección.
